I"·ê<p>Now, we begin.</p>

<p>And indeed, once again, greetings unto you, beloved and holy friends.
<em>Indeed, greetings to you, beloved and holy friends.</em> If you understand
the meaning of this greeting, if you comprehend the <em>depth</em> of each term
used, already you know all there is to know. And you are well prepared
