if it flows <em>through</em> you, it must first flow <em>to</em> you. Therefore, seek
always to <em>receive</em> in order to <em>give</em>. For what can you give another if you
have not yet given it to yourself?</p>

<p>How many of you have been taught to try to love, to try to do the
‚Äúright‚Äù thing, the ‚Äúgood‚Äù thing? ‚Ä¶whatever that is supposed to mean.
And yet, how many times have you gone within your secret chamber and
