<blockquote>
  <p>Yes, I accept your presence in my life. I turn the whole thing over.
Now, each moment is dedicated to healing and awakening the illusory
sense of separation from God that once I created in error.</p>
</blockquote>

<p>Love! In how many ways have you sought it? Hmm! Can you count the ways?
Hmm! Would you dare to try to count each little pebble of sand on the
